== Chiba kerde andar aver puraneder chiba ==
Yek angluni chib si yek chib savyatar aven le chiba yeke [[chhibavipnaski familiya|chibavipenaske familiyake]]. Varesave anglune chiba janglyoven mishto, ama aver si palem kerde andar familiyake chiba sar thoven pen godyate ke sas. Kadya si i [[Angluni Indo-Europikani chhib|Angluni Indo-Evropikani]], i [[Angluni Bantu chhib|Angluni Bantu Chib]]

== Yek vakyaripnasko sistemo may sira pherdo sar yek chachi chib ==
Yek angluni chib so nay lake:
* yek zorali, pherdi sintaksa;
* kernavnenge (verbonge) vaxta, navnenge paruvimata, th.a.
* yek  zoralo lavustik (vokabularo).

